markdownRemark.html: We know a great deal more about the circumstances of Mancinelli's teaching, especially late in his career, since Dugald McLellan has located and published a very rich series of documents concerning Mancinelli's stint in Orvieto. See his Antonio Mancinelli ad Orvieto (2014), cit. above at section 3.0 par. 1.
